          exercise: "Take the 7-Day Positivity Challenge! Every day for one week, do one of these kind things online: Day 1 — Leave three genuine compliments on friends' posts. Day 2 — Share something that made you smile or laugh. Day 3 — Send a kind private message to someone you have not talked to in a while. Day 4 — Thank someone publicly for something they did that helped you. Day 5 — Post something encouraging for anyone who might be having a hard day. Day 6 — Share a post from a small creator or friend who deserves more attention. Day 7 — Write a post about something you are grateful for and tag the people involved. Track how these acts of kindness make YOU feel in a little journal!",
